Package
Description
fr.u_paris.gla.project.astar
Astar package provides an implementation of Astar algorithm for the path findingo of our application.
fr.u_paris.gla.project.controllers
Controllers package provides controllers for the GUI in order to handle actions and link model to gui.
fr.u_paris.gla.project.graph
Graph package provides the model for our application, the representation of the network as java objects.
fr.u_paris.gla.project.utils
Utils package provides helper functions and classes to parse CSV, calculates distances, manage transport types, etc...
fr.u_paris.gla.project.views
views package provides classes for the Graphical User Interface and its components.
